Minimum spec Required

Processor: 1 Ghz. Memory: 1024 MB RAM. Graphics: OpenGL 2.1 must be supported by your video card. July 2, 2006 - any graphics card manufatured before that will not work.
Very cheap pc in order to run game, so performance should not be a major concern
OpenGL (Open Graphics Library) is a cross-language, cross-platform application programming interface (API) for rendering 2D and 3D vector graphics
